      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 18,
      "message": "Processing of \"<<:\", \"*x\", and \"&x\" is part of the YAML parse,  processing of \"{y}\" is part of the jjb processing and is done after the YAML parse, so this should work as long as everything that pulls this in with \"<<:\" also sets docker-root.",
